<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[الذَّنْبُ]</span>: الجُرْمُ،<span class="c5"> وجمعه:</span> ذنوب،<span class="c5"> قال الله تعالى:</span> غاافِرِ الذَّنْبِ <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فَعَلٌ]</span>، بفتح العين<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
